Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has become a superhuman society,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and about 80% of the world's population\Nnow has some kind of special trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world swirling with chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the profession that everyone\Nonce dreamed about and admired
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came into the limelight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes of justice fighting villains\Nand saving people from distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the story of\Nhow I became the greatest hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first match of the first round\Nof the finals tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Izuku Midoriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From general studies, it's Hitoshi Shinso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Force your opponent out of bounds,\Nor immobilize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also win by making\Nyour opponent say, "I give up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I give up," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fight to test\Nthe strength of your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know what you want for your future,\Nthen you can't worry about appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That monkey was going on about his pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but don't you think he was\Ndumb for throwing away his chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through the trouble of warning him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Deku?!\N--It's the important first match! Liven things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What in the world is going on?\N--It's the important first match! Liven things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya! The match just started...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he's completely frozen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a blank look on his face\Nand isn't moving a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Shinso's Quirk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't stand out {\i1}at all{\i0},\Nbut could he actually be someone amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Victory or Defeat"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitoshi Shinso from general studies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has gotten the better of\NIzuku Midoriya from the hero course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've imagined this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the bottom really overthrow the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said the\Nentrance exam wasn't rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some basic data on the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's individual matches from here\Non out, I had someone compile it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:54.50,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hitoshi Shinso\NGeneral Studies\NClass 1-C Nabooh Middle School"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinso failed the practical exam\Nfor the hero course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he also applied for general studies,\Nhe probably knew that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Quirk is very powerful, but the practical\Nexam consisted of fighting faux villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gave an advantage to\Nthose with physical attack Quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinso wouldn't have been able\Nto rack up any points with his Quirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky that you've\Nbeen blessed, Izuku Midoriya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around and walk out of bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya's being so obedient!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deku, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go out of bounds,\Nthen you'll lose the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Quirk is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hitoshi Shinso"\N"Quirk: Brainwashing"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitoshi Shinso. Quirk: Brainwashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answering his question turns on a\Nbrainwashing switch in his opponent's brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forcing them to do what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't want the brainwashing\Nswitch to turn on, it won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the fitness test on the first day of school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya scored pretty low for the hero course,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even in tests where he didn't use his Quirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he did better than Shinso.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if they fight normally,\Nthen Midoriya would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can just overcome Shinso's Brainwashing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way, this'll end quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Midoriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ahhhhhhhhhhhh"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My body's moving on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like... my head's filled with fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though... Even though Ojiro warned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Waiting Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Quirk that can control people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that too strong to beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you can probably\Navoid if you know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember much\Nafter I answered his question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I answer without thinking,\Nthen I'll lose right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but it's not completely impenetrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I barely remembered\Nanything until almost the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were running away after\NShinso stole Tetsutetsu's headband,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I ran into one of\Nthe horses on Team Tetsutetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I snapped out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember what happened clearly after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So receiving a shock can get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I don't know\Nwhat level of shock you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in a one-on-one match, you can't\Ncount on outside forces like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's about all I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to say something selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but please do your best for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone is counting on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... {\i1}is{\i0}... this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mov...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even with a Quirk like this,\NI have my own dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, lose for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya's stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fingers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he remove the brainwashing\Nby making them explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be able to move freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who discharged my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't the one who moved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People I didn't know came to mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and for a second, my mind was clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passed on to me like a sacred torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The presence of the people\Nwho spun together this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they save me? Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I think about it now,\NI won't find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later... Thinking can come later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't answer... Did he figure out my secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he should've heard from\Nthat monkey from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is make him talk again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can produce that much\Npower just by moving your fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt the same way in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my Quirk,\NI've been behind from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who's been blessed like\Nyou can't understand, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}do{\i0} understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's true... I've been blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you who was\Nborn with the ideal Quirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who can reach your goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been blessed by others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lose, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to push me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinso is out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya advances to round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Three Years Ago"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nabooh City Middle School"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Shinso, your Quirk is Brainwashing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! I've never heard of that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you can control anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do as much bad stuff as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one'd know it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't control us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if someone else had it, the first thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think is that they'd use it for evil, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Criminal"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's good for being a villain, huh?"\NI'm used to people insinuating that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what the world is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the finals, the first person\Nto advance to the second round
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Izuku Midoriya from Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning the tables at the last moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Midoriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did that shoulder toss\Non you before, too, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Dunce Face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was definitely aiming for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He led him right into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using his power on part of\Nhis body like at the fitness test
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the throw from the combat training...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than calling it the\Nbest use of his experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like he's using any experience he\Ncan to force the flow to change in his favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:08.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Izuku Midoriya"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was kind of a boring first match,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we should praise them\Nboth for a bravely fought match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who's been blessed\Nlike you can't understand, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who can reach your goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinso, why do you want to be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help the things you long for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt the same way before\NI inherited One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I say right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were really cool, Shinso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the star of general studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put up a great fight against the guy\Nwho placed first in the obstacle course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Quirk would work quite\Nwell against villains. I wish I had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U.A.'s not very smart\Nif he's in general studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they've got a ton of people applying,\Nso some things just can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the difference in combat experience, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it ends up making a big difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that, Shinso?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the results, they'll consider\Nour transfer into the hero course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it didn't work this time,\NI definitely won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get into the hero course, get certified,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll definitely become\Na better hero than you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the match is over, what's he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are usually wary\Nwhen they talk to me, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, someone'll trip you up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't lose in an unseemly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Recovery Girl's Temporary Nurse's Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the match with Shinso,\NI couldn't smile at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his cries hit close to home for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't mean that I could lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means\Nto aim for number one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put some weird pressure\Non him again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was necessary! Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were eight or nine people...\NI'm not sure exactly how many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it felt like my mind was\Nfilled with fog from the brainwashing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the vision appeared,\Nas if to drive away the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like I was barely able to move\Njust my fingertips for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone with\Neyes like you, too, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it... the people who had\Ninherited One For All who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary... What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought you'd know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I also saw it before, in my younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clear sign that you've got\Na better grasp on One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's like a trace of something\Nthey left behind in One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something with intent\Nthat can interfere with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you can't interfere with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that vision isn't\Nwhat got rid of the brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that when you saw the vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your strong emotions allowed you to\Novercome Young Shinso's Brainwashing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for just long enough\Nto move your fingertips, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explanation's not\Nsatisfying at all, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too hung up about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, don't you need\Nto go see who you'll fight next?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:49.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Recovery Girl's Temporary Nurse's Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you both very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... were there, too, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Player Waiting Room 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya won, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting disgracefully, Shoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you used the power in your left side,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've had an overwhelming victory in the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,obstacle course and the cavalry battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this childish rebellion already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a duty to surpass All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're different from your siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the greatest masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you can say, bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will win and advance with just Mom's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use your power when I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that works for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll soon reach the limits of that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Deku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saved a seat for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is... these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shoto Todoroki" "Hanta Sero"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good! He's good, but what's\Nwith that plainness he just can't get rid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Hanta Sero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking second, then first in the prelims!\NYou're way too strong, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't recommended for admission for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also from the hero course, it's Shoto Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, for the second match of the finals--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ready... Start!\N--Well, I don't feel like I can win...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't feel like losing, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A surprise attack aimed\Nto push his opponent out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that was the\Nbest choice for this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, get him, Sero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this vibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sero, can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sero is immobilized!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Todoroki advances to the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't worry about it!\N--Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I went overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the eyes of the crowd that started\Nshouting "Don't worry about it" unprompted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was Todoroki, melting what\Nhe'd frozen himself with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he looked very sad to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The preview is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The U.A. sports festival finals tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sixteen players in it clash\Nwith their Quirks and their pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only a slight difference\Nbetween winning and losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who can win
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are those who train diligently every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hang on to their dream of becoming a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, you zygotes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Battle on, Challengers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Iida is manipulated by a girl\Nand is completely humiliated!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:51.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next time: Battle on, Challengers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Ultra!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
